{"id":47624,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":12,"day":9}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"186","ytitle":"","mtitle":"诗二首","ftitle":"","authors":["蓝兵"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深宵:我底沉绿枪做着梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里的血花是开遍了的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个恐怖的夜静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一回杀敌心脏的跳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你觉得那是奇怪的错觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我穿着起古老的夜行衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里飞越过山野:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高月黑瞧我追杀敌兵!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有长长的年月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我流落在江南；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南是柔情之国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今也驰骋着战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵夜冷霜寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也唱起‘还我河山!’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遂记起有山的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也燃起了万里烽火——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用号角吹奏‘夜在塞上’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤坟荒野闪耀战血斑斑……"}]}